<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/27056697">如何评价微博热门话题「#领导请你尊重这门专业#」？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3005593" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"><a class=" wrap external" href="http://weibo.com/p/100808a7ffd4560be2d7ce068c3d81ab9cde23?k=%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%AF%B7%E4%BD%A0%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E8%BF%99%E9%97%A8%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A&amp;from=526&amp;_from_=huati_topic" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">#领导请你尊重这门专业#<i class="icon-external"></i></a></div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

<a href="#" name="addcomment" class="toggle-comment meta-item">
